Name: Reach the Moon!
About the game: Don't repeat this at home! The game Reach the Moon! it is an experiment & casual game in same time. The main character is a bodybuilder which with the help of his enormous biceps throws a man into the air. His main goal is to make the man reach the galaxy. Will he be able to see the earth from above? Game Features : - Distance calculator - The chance to surpass the moon - A strong bodybuilder
